high_descs: walk to face counter to left of sink
pick up spoon from counter top
wash spoon in sink, pick up spoon from sink
walk to face black shelves left of the sink
put spoon onto to of black shelves under the lettuce
anns.task_desc: put a washed spoon on black shelves

high_descs: go to the Turn around and go across the kitchen, to the stove, then turn to your right, and go to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the fork on the counter, that is laying across two forks.
Go to the sink to your immediate right.
Place the spoon in the sink, turn the water on, rinse off the spoon, turn the water off, and remove the spoon from the sink.
Turn to your left and go to the small, black stand on the right side of the kitchen counter.
Place the spoon on the small, black stand, behind the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon on the black stand.

high_descs: Turn around go toward the stove, then turn right to face the counter next to the sink.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
Go to the sink to your right.
Clean the spoon inside of the sink.
Turn around and move forward, then turn right, then turn right again to face the black table.
Put the spoon on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon on the black table.
